title: 关于ChestCommands打开环球市场
author: Withered_Boss
txt_content: 通过菜单执行market listings打开环球市场后GUI里什么都没有 怎么办

replies.author: xRPQx
replies.txt_content:
请在里面加入一条
   KEEP-OPEN: true

replies.author: Withered_Boss
replies.txt_content:
qq1812538626 发表于 2015-9-1 12:58
请在里面加入一条
   KEEP-OPEN: true
a10001323:
  NAME: '&b打开全球市场'
  LORE:
    - '&d方便的交易市场'
    - '&d购买的物品储存到邮箱'
  ID: 130
  COMMAND: 'market listings'
  KEEP-OPEN: true
  POSITION-X: 1
  POSITION-Y: 1
